@startuml platform-tracing-03-api-module
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"

title platform-tracing-api — публичный контракт (framework-agnostic)

package "space.br1440.platform.tracing.api" as root #FFF8E1 {

  interface PlatformTracing {
    +currentTraceId(): Optional<String>
    +currentSpanId(): Optional<String>
    +startSpan(name, category): SpanScope
    +startHttpServer/Client/Db/Rpc/Internal()
    +recordException(throwable)
  }

  interface SpanScope <<AutoCloseable>> {
    +setAttribute(key, value)
    +addEvent(name)
    +setResult(SpanResult)
    +recordException(throwable)
    +close()
  }

  enum SpanCategory {
    HTTP_SERVER
    HTTP_CLIENT
    DATABASE
    RPC
    INTERNAL
    PLATFORM
  }

  enum SpanResult {
    SUCCESS
    FAILURE
  }

  class PlatformAttributes <<utility>> {
    +PLATFORM_TYPE
    +PLATFORM_RESULT
    +PLATFORM_REMOTE_SERVICE
    +PLATFORM_C_GROUP
    +HTTP_*, DB_*, RPC_* (semconv aliases)
  }

  class PlatformHeaders <<utility>> {
    +X_TRACE_ON
    +X_QA_TRACE
    +X_REQUEST_ID
    +X_TRACE_ID
  }

  class TracingMdcKeys <<utility>> {
    +traceId / spanId / traceFlags
  }

  record TracingRequestContext {
    correlationId
    traceId
    spanId
  }

  annotation Traced
  annotation TracedAttribute
}

package "spi" as spi_pkg #FFECB3 {
  interface SpanEnricher <<SPI>> {
    +enrich(SpanScope)
  }
  interface SensitiveDataRule <<SPI>> {
    +name()
    +priority()
    +matches(key, value)
    +mask(key, value)
  }
  interface SamplingDecisionContributor <<SPI>> {
    +priority()
    +decide(name, attrs): Optional<Decision>
  }
}

PlatformTracing ..> SpanScope : creates
PlatformTracing ..> SpanCategory
SpanScope ..> SpanResult
SpanScope ..> PlatformAttributes : writes

note bottom of root
  **Зависимости Gradle**
  • api: jakarta.annotation-api
  • compileOnly: lombok
  **Намеренно отсутствуют:** Spring, Micrometer, OTel SDK
end note

note right of spi_pkg
  **SPI без ServiceLoader в api**
  Реализации подключаются:
  • otel-extension: ServiceLoader<SensitiveDataRule>
  • SamplingDecisionContributor — задекларирован,\n  но в CompositeSampler пока не wired
  **→ кандидат на рефакторинг SPI-реестра**
end note

@enduml


@startuml platform-tracing-04-core-module
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"

title platform-tracing-core — адаптация PlatformTracing → OpenTelemetry API

class DefaultPlatformTracing {
  -tracer: Tracer
  +INSTRUMENTATION_NAME = "space.br1440.platform.tracing"
  __
  +DefaultPlatformTracing(OpenTelemetry)
  +startSpan() → OtelSpanScope
  +recordException()
  -toSpanKind(SpanCategory): SpanKind
}

class "OtelSpanScope\n(private inner)" as OtelSpanScope {
  -span: Span
  -scope: Scope
  +setAttribute / setResult / close()
}

class NoOpPlatformTracing <<singleton>> {
  +INSTANCE
  +startSpan() → NoOpSpanScope
}

interface PlatformTracing
interface SpanScope

PlatformTracing <|.. DefaultPlatformTracing
PlatformTracing <|.. NoOpPlatformTracing
DefaultPlatformTracing +-- OtelSpanScope
SpanScope <|.. OtelSpanScope

DefaultPlatformTracing --> "OpenTelemetry\n.getTracer()" : uses
OtelSpanScope --> "Span.makeCurrent()\nSpan.end()" : context propagation

note top of DefaultPlatformTracing
  **Поток создания span**
  1. tracer.spanBuilder(name)
  2. setSpanKind + platform.type attribute
  3. startSpan → makeCurrent
  4. close → scope.close + span.end
end note

note bottom of NoOpPlatformTracing
  Активируется TracingCoreAutoConfiguration когда:
  • нет OpenTelemetry bean
  • GlobalOpenTelemetry — noop (probe span invalid)
  Гарантирует безопасную деградацию без agent.
end note

note as N_obs
  **ObservationConvention'ы**
  Намеренно НЕ в core — только в autoconfigure.
  Core остаётся usable вне Spring (unit tests, CLI).
end note

@enduml


@startuml platform-tracing-05-otel-extension
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"

title platform-tracing-otel-extension — расширение OpenTelemetry Java Agent

package "META-INF/services" as meta #F3E5F5 {
  file "AutoConfigurationCustomizerProvider" as acp
  file "ResourceProvider" as rp
}

package "configuration" as cfg {
  class PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer {
    +customize(AutoConfigurationCustomizer)
    -platformDefaults(): Map
    -buildSampler(): CompositeSampler
    -registerSpanProcessors(): SdkTracerProviderBuilder
    -collectScrubbingRules(): List<SensitiveDataRule>
    -tryRegisterMBean()
  }
  class ExtensionPropertyNames <<constants>>
  class ExtensionDefaults <<constants>>
  class PlatformTracingDefaultsProvider
  class AutoConfigurationCustomizerOrdering
}

package "sampler" as samp {
  class CompositeSampler {
    +shouldSample()
    -- priority --
    1. X-Trace-On force
    2. X-QA-Trace force
    3. url.path drop prefixes
    4. delegate (MutableRatioSampler)
  }
  class MutableRatioSampler
}

package "processor" as proc {
  class EnrichingSpanProcessor
  class ScrubbingSpanProcessor
  class ValidatingSpanProcessor
  class SpanWatchdogProcessor
  class SafeSpanProcessor <<wrapper>>
}

package "scrubbing.rules" as rules {
  class BuiltInSensitiveDataRules
  class EmailRule
  class JwtRule
  class PasswordKeyRule
  class PanRule
  class PhoneRule
  class IbanRule / InnRule / SnilsRule
}

package "resource" as res {
  class PlatformResourceProvider
}

package "jmx" as jmx {
  class PlatformTracingControl
  interface PlatformTracingControlMBean
}

acp --> PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer
rp --> PlatformResourceProvider

PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer --> CompositeSampler
PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer --> EnrichingSpanProcessor
PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer --> ScrubbingSpanProcessor
PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer --> ValidatingSpanProcessor
PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer --> SpanWatchdogProcessor
SafeSpanProcessor ..> proc : wraps\n(isolates failures)

ScrubbingSpanProcessor --> SensitiveDataRule
BuiltInSensitiveDataRules --> rules
PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer ..> "ServiceLoader\n<SensitiveDataRule>" : custom rules

MutableRatioSampler --> PlatformTracingControl : registered via JMX
PlatformTracingControl ..> PlatformTracingControlMBean

note right of PlatformAutoConfigurationCustomizer
  **Pipeline SpanProcessor (onEnd)**
  enriching → scrubbing → validation → watchdog
  Каждый обёрнут SafeSpanProcessor.
end note

note bottom of PlatformTracingDefaultsProvider
  **Два namespace конфигурации**
  platform.tracing.* — доменные ключи extension
  otel.bsp.* / otel.span.* — SDK defaults через addPropertiesSupplier
  Приоритет: OTEL_* env > -D > SPI defaults
end note

@enduml


