note as N_cond
  **Условная активация (@Conditional*)**
  • platform.tracing.enabled (default true)
  • @ConditionalOnWebApplication SERVLET | REACTIVE
  • @ConditionalOnClass Servlet / WebFlux / Aspect / Actuator
  • @ConditionalOnBean MeterRegistry (metrics decorator)
  Servlet и Reactive co-exist in one JAR — stack chosen at runtime.
end note

note as N_cfg_dup
  **TracingProperties vs agent configuration**
  Дубли: sampling.ratio, scrubbing, limits, serviceNames.
  Spring-app читает TracingProperties;
  Agent-extension читает ConfigProperties (OTEL_ / -D).
  Синхронизация сейчас — соглашение + Helm, не единый binder.
end note

